<h2>SSL</h2>

<h3>Binary Version</h3>

<p>Within the file one <i>TOMCAT/webapps/yanel/WEB-INF/web.xml</i> can set</p>

<p>
&lt;servlet><br/>
   ...<br/>
  &lt;init-param xmlns:webApp="http://java.sun.com/xml/ns/j2ee"><br/>
    &lt;param-name>ssl-port&lt;/param-name><br/>
    &lt;param-value>8443&lt;/param-value><br/>
  &lt;/init-param><br/>
&lt;/servlet><br/>
</p>

<h3>Source Version</h3>

<p>
Within the file src/build/(local.)build.properties one can set the parameters tomcat1.ssl.port=8443 and tomcat2.ssl.port=8443. The re-configure (run "configure" to make Tomcat SSL aware within "conf/server.xml") resp. re-build (run "build" to patch the "web.xml" file) Yanel
</p>
</body>
